data.title: PRTM Global Supply Chain Trends - Oct08
data.meta_description: PRTM Global Supply Chain Trends_Oct08 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. The annual Supply Chain Trends study has been modified from a regional to a global focus. The purpose of the study is to provide supply chain executives with an understanding of the key Supply Chain Trends. The majority of survey participants are companies with annual revenues greater than $1 billion.
